# Verify Integrity Workflow

1. // turbo
   Run `npm run lint` to check for code style issues.
2. // turbo
   Run `npm run type-check` (tsc --noEmit) to check for TypeScript errors.
3. // turbo
   Run `npm run test` to run unit and integration tests.
4. // turbo
   Run `npm run test:e2e` to run end-to-end tests (headless).
5. Report the summary of results. If any step fails, stop and report the error.
